&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">_display_errors = Off_&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>Para On&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Apache restrito httpd.conf</title><link>https://sidneiweber.com.br/apache-restrito-httpdconf/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Sep 2009 18:51:29 -0300</pubDate><guid>https://sidneiweber.com.br/apache-restrito-httpdconf/</guid><description>&lt;p>Exemplo de como restringir o acesso com apache realizando autenticação no LDAP.&lt;/p>
